  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Other Side Of Mist And Mountain is a Japanese-style horror mystery adventure game.</h2>The game's story blends elements of horror, mystery, deduction, and folk tales. Gameplay is primarily based on visual novels, enriched with interactive scenes and puzzle-solving mechanisms. Through meticulously crafted scripts, it presents a series of captivating and enigmatic stories that will tug at your heartstrings.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672060/extras/dd57deb5543f843f0e1c5ea0db833a99.avif?t=1725468643\" width=600 height=94 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672060/extras/b1df53120941e62d7c2abe9b1e0c3584.avif?t=1725468643\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br>Five years ago, sophomore student Maha Igarashi took a late-night train to Soukyo City to attend a social flash mob event organized by an occult forum. She disappeared midway after getting off at a station called Kisaragi, and the station itself vanished thereafter. Maha's boyfriend, Shizuno Yokoyama, never stopped searching for her. He opened a detective agency in his hometown, specializing in peculiar requests, all in pursuit of clues to find Maha. As his investigation deepens, he finds himself increasingly entangled in the mist of mysteries...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672060/extras/505dc03d6e1a155a515b252036dcc536.avif?t=1725468643\" width=600 height=94 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore diverse maps, engage in dialogues, and investigate clues within scenes.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672060/extras/fde287882fc33222f8f0faec669b7f3f.poster.avif?t=1725468643\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672060/extras/fde287882fc33222f8f0faec669b7f3f.webm?t=1725468643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672060/extras/fde287882fc33222f8f0faec669b7f3f.mp4?t=1725468643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Interact with mechanisms to solve puzzles.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672060/extras/7f8a4d61be2b9f0aa0fbccfe13dbb185.poster.avif?t=1725468643\" width=598 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672060/extras/7f8a4d61be2b9f0aa0fbccfe13dbb185.webm?t=1725468643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672060/extras/7f8a4d61be2b9f0aa0fbccfe13dbb185.mp4?t=1725468643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Make different choices to trigger various storylines.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672060/extras/9bb532824c80294da462c7e1dd8fa5ed.avif?t=1725468643\" width=600 height=240 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Investigate various peculiar supernatural requests.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672060/extras/9ea5e4aac4adae75e7b102f77edf8c36.avif?t=1725468643\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2672060/extras/a0666df2b43cd37488418a866b526364.avif?t=1725468643\" width=600 height=94 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"